data.description: Lovely brick and stone home with 4 bedrooms and 3 baths. Wonderfully designed floor plan with effortless flow between rooms. Designer and architectural details and privacy blinds througout. All bedrooms are spacious with great closet space. Front guest bedroom makes a great office/study. Formal dining room and formal living room will accomodate all of your guests. Kitchen features granite counters, breakfast bar, rich wood cabinets w/hardware, 5 burner gas burner range, and adjoining breakfast room. Family room with beautiful tray ceiling and tiled gas fireplace with mantel. Primary suite with soaring ceilings and private ensuite bath w/double sinks, vanity, separate shower, tub, & walk in closet. Covered back patio accessible from the breakfast room & primary bedroom. Neighborhood amenities included 2 pools, beautiful lakes, walking & biking trails, basketball court, & several pocket parks. Great location w/convenient access to Westpark Tollway, Grand Parkway, shopping, & restaurants.
